{"tid":431362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔公路5車串燒　鐵騎休班藍帽子慘死","createTime":"2017-10-10T15:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T16:23:37.000Z","uid":20058,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac6ad83497339fdce019ce37a948923db2db458","tid":431362,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"【21：34】慘死輪下的鐵騎士姓曾(28歲)，是新界南總區警察機動部隊(PTU)一名休班男警員，由新界南總部收工回家途中遇上車禍。 <br />\n<br />\n沙田發生致命交通意外。晚上近8時，一輛電單車及一輛寶馬房車，先後沿大埔公路沙田段快線往大埔方向行駛，至近禾輋邨美和樓對開，2車因應前面交通情況收慢，隨後的福士及奧迪私家車亦及時減速，惟尾隨一輛四驅車疑收掣不及，猛撼前車將其推前釀5車串燒。 <br />\n<br />\n因撞擊力猛烈，鐵騎士捱撞後倒地疑遭車輛輾過，再被福士左車頭及寶馬車尾夾爆頭重創。救護員接報趕至，經檢查後證實鐵騎士當場死亡，用白布遮蓋死者遺體。警方封鎖路面調查，現場遺下大攤血漬，爆裂頭盔跌在一旁，另有車輛組件散落路面。事後一名司機報稱不適，需由救護車送院檢查。 <br />\n<br />\n受意外影響，運輸署宣布，大埔公路沙田段往大埔方向全線封閉，車龍龍尾至大圍隧道及城門隧道。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171010/mobile/bkn-20171010202027657-1010_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171010%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171010202027657-1010_00822_001.html&d=ZMIILXoNzp4iQkVGFJjd%2BzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=9ff4b53c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171010/mobile/bkn-20171010202027657-1010_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2d7a684ac3bc4c0dd1be990f36dfdf97a5c0e9b1","tid":431362,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T15:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n口徳撚請進場"},{"pid":"1dfdb6403a18e655cf3fdb04ee73bf5c7aa52578","tid":431362,"uid":12449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T15:21:12.000Z","msg":"因禍得福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d547ef61149900740039d35ea67a8f83b24e9e1","tid":431362,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e211cd576aa6a72f90f79ac8a9ff568fb991e94","tid":431362,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"唉唷唷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d826c98029350158e3f74a840eef24ec04ddd4","tid":431362,"uid":5637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:05:49.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674e7335b6a0cdbec933b00b3ca4e3d431450057","tid":431362,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"Roadkill"}]}